Package ca.ualberta.lard.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Comment
    An instance of Comment represents a comment a user creates to share her thoughts about a particular location.
    CommentRequest
    A CommentRequest is a structure that aids in the retrieving of comments.
    DataModel
    DataModel is the data abstraction layer of the application.
    GeoLocation
    A GeoLocation is composed of a latitude and a longitude, and as the name suggests it represents a location in the world.
    GeoLocationMap
    A GeoLocation map of specific latitude, longitude pairs of locations on the University of Alberta campus.
    Picture
    Simple picture model
    User
    The User model deals with the unique username of the user.
